The paper discusses a new style of temporal debugging and a new debugger called URDB that supports multiple programming languages and architectures. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, given that the paper focuses on debugging techniques and tools, cs.SE is the most likely sub-category.
